Name: Switch It
About the game: A bit frustrating game where you have to reach the end using the different types of blocks that you have. -You have unlimited attempts to complete the game. -You can't save game. -Use the checkpoints so you don't have to start from the beginning. -Use the different blocks wisely. -Go to the end without crying.
